    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This is not possible without modifying the name, although I think the following  should be allowed:\r\n\r\n```\r\npragma solidity ^0.4.13;\r\n\r\ncontract Example {\r\n    struct myStruct {\r\n        uint myInt;\r\n        bool myBool;\r\n        bytes32[] myArr;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    myStruct expose;\r\n\r\n    function expose() external returns (bool) {\r\n        return expose.myBool;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhat do you think, @axic?",
